    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "from mpl_toolkits.mplot3d import Axes3D # Import Axes3D for 3D plots\n",
        "\n",
        "dates = pd.date_range(\"20130101\", periods=100)\n",
        "df = pd.DataFrame(np.random.randn(100, 4), index=dates, columns=list(\"ABCD\"))\n",
        "\n",
        "x = np.arange(len(df)) # X-axis: Data point index\n",
        "y = np.arange(len(df.columns)) # Y-axis: Column index\n",
        "X, Y = np.meshgrid(x, y) # Create meshgrid for X and Y\n",
        "Z = df.values # Z-axis: Data values\n",
        "\n",
        "fig = plt.figure(figsize=(10, 8)) # Adjust figure size for better visualization\n",
        "ax = fig.add_subplot(111, projection='3d') # Create a 3D subplot\n",
        "\n",
        "# Create the 3D bar plot\n",
        "dx = dy = 0.8 # Width and depth of bars\n",
        "dz = Z # Height of bars\n",
        "ax.bar3d(X.ravel(), Y.ravel(), np.zeros_like(Z.ravel()), dx, dy, dz.ravel(), color='b', alpha=0.5)\n",
        "\n",
        "# Customize the plot\n",
        "ax.set_xlabel('Data Point Index')\n",
        "ax.set_ylabel('Column Index')\n",
        "ax.set_zlabel('Data Value')\n",
        "ax.set_title('3D Bar Plot of DataFrame')\n",
        "\n",
        "plt.show()\n"
      ],
      "metadata": {

      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import matplotlib.pyplot as plt\n",
        "dates = pd.date_range(\"20130101\", periods=100)\n",
        "df = pd.DataFrame(np.random.randn(100, 4), index=dates,\n",
        "columns=list(\"ABCD\"))\n",
        "%matplotlib inline\n",
        "sns.set_style(\"darkgrid\")\n",
        "matplotlib.rcParams['font.size'] = 14\n",
        "matplotlib.rcParams['figure.figsize'] = (9, 5)\n",
        "matplotlib.rcParams['figure.facecolor'] = '#00000000'\n",
        "# Generate a correlation matrix for the selected columns\n",
        "corrMatrix = df.corr()\n",
        "# Plot the correlation matrix using a heatmap\n",
        "plt.figure(figsize=(10,10))\n",
        "sns.heatmap(corrMatrix, annot=True)\n",
        "plt.show()"
      ],

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import numpy as np\n",
        "from scipy import stats\n",
        "# 三個班學生的成績\n",
        "group1 = [85, 86, 88, 75, 78, 94]\n",
        "group2 = [92, 94, 89, 96, 93, 95, 76, 50]\n",
        "group3 = [78, 81, 79, 84, 77, 80]\n",
        "# 使用 scipy.stats.f_oneway 進行單因子 ANOVA 檢定\n",
        "f_statistic, p_value = stats.f_oneway(group1, group2, group3)\n",
        "# 輸出結果\n",
        "print(\"F 統計量:\", f_statistic)\n",
        "print(\"p-value:\", p_value)\n",
        "# 解釋結果\n",
        "alpha = 0.05 # 顯著性水平\n",
        "if p_value < alpha:\n",
        " print(\"拒絕原假設：不同組別之間的均值存在顯著差異。\")\n",
        "else:\n",
        " print(\"未能拒絕原假設：不同組別之間的均值沒有顯著差異。\")"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "qJFmImYd9xJi",
        "outputId": "f818cd99-8b22-4e00-f106-04727b59720d"
      },
      "execution_count": null,
      "outputs": [
        {
          "output_type": "stream",
          "name": "stdout",
          "text": [
            "F 統計量: 0.5135486690669941\n",
            "p-value: 0.6073604385431465\n",
            "未能拒絕原假設：不同組別之間的均值沒有顯著差異。\n"
          ]
        }
      ]

    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "source": [
        "import pandas as pd\n",
        "import statsmodels.api as sm\n",
        "from statsmodels.formula.api import ols\n",
        "# 創建數據集\n",
        "data = {\n",
        "'Score': [85, 86, 88, 75, 78, 94, 92, 94, 89, 96, 93, 95, 78, 81,\n",
        "79, 84, 77, 80],\n",
        "'Method': ['A', 'A', 'A', 'A', 'A', 'A', # 教學方法 A\n",
        "'B', 'B', 'B', 'B', 'B', 'B', # 教學方法 B\n",
        "'C', 'C', 'C', 'C', 'C', 'C'] # 教學方法 C\n",
        "}\n",
        "# 將數據轉換為 DataFrame\n",
        "df = pd.DataFrame(data)\n",
        "# 使用 statsmodels 中的 ols 方法進行單因子 ANOVA 分析\n",
        "model = ols('Score ~ C(Method)', data=df).fit()\n",
        "anova_table = sm.stats.anova_lm(model, typ=2)\n",
        "# 輸出 ANOVA 表\n",
        "print(anova_table)\n",
        "df"
      ],
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/",

              "      async function convertToInteractive(key) {\n",
              "        const element = document.querySelector('#df-f7456735-4a72-442b-840f-aeb706df9c52');\n",
              "        const dataTable =\n",
              "          await google.colab.kernel.invokeFunction('convertToInteractive',\n",
              "                                                    [key], {});\n",
              "        if (!dataTable) return;\n",
              "\n",
              "        const docLinkHtml = 'Like what you see? Visit the ' +\n",
              "          '<a target=\"_blank\" href=https://colab.research.google.com/notebooks/data_table.ipynb>data table notebook</a>'\n",
              "          + ' to learn more about interactive tables.';\n",
              "        element.innerHTML = '';\n",
              "        dataTable['output_type'] = 'display_data';\n",
              "        await google.colab.output.renderOutput(dataTable, element);\n",
              "        const docLink = document.createElement('div');\n",
              "        docLink.innerHTML = docLinkHtml;\n",
              "        element.appendChild(docLink);\n",
              "      }\n",
              "    </script>\n",
              "  </div>\n",
